diangkat sisa-sisa selnya.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>(Diadaptasi dari https://hellosehat.com/hidup-sehat/fakta-unik/kanker-dan-tumor-apa-bedanya-sih/)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/MBpUUTNSIdlwoLrVtzwOHbXnzPb1w_1w3H_aAPT_Y34Ygu_J_IhKfPllA5nnZQd9vf-FUUG-04ijjzXXnanyBBkP59QuxG5tqvvJZzV7OpdshxLdf-TNgGJ8Q8rznzD5-ElTYX0\" xss=removed></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Berdasarkan paragraf 2, manakah pernyataan di bawah ini yang PALING MUNGKIN benar?</span></span></span></p>', '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Struktur otak dapat dilindungi dari kerusakan tumor jika tumor tersebut segera diobati dengan tepat.</span></span></span></p>', '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Tumor jinak yang berukuran besar sama berbahayanya dengan kanker.</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Sel-sel kanker akan selalu kambuh di tempat yang sama seperti sebelumnya.</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Tumor jinak hanya akan menyerang sel-sel otak saja.</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Kanker tidak mungkin menyerang sel-sel otak.</span></span></span></p>', 1, '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Kunci Jawabannya adalah </span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><strong>(A)</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Pembahasan</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Simpulan yang paling mungkin benar dari paragraf 2 adalah jawaban A.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>