(28, 6, 4, '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Gas asetilena dapat dihasilkan dari reaksi berikut:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>CaC<sub>2(g) </sub>+ 2 H<sub>2</sub>O<sub>(l) </sub> </span><span xss=removed>à</span><span xss=removed> Ca(OH)<sub>2(aq) </sub>+ C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>2(g)</sub></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Nilai kalor pembakaran gas yang dimaksud adalah – 320 kkal mol<sup>-1</sup>. Jika dalam suatu proses digunakan 128 gram kalsium karbida dan dengan asumsi bahwa hanya 75 ?C<sub>2</sub> yang bereaksi, maka pada pembakaran gas etilena yang terbentuk akan dihasilkan kalor sebanyak …. (Diketahui Ar C = 12; Ca = 40; H = 1; dan O = 16)</span></span></span></p>', '<p>320 kkal</p>', '<p>480 kkal</p>', '<p>640 kkal</p>', '<p>800 kkal</p>', '<p>960 kkal</p>', 2, '<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table\" xss=removed>\r\n <tbody>\r\n  <tr>\r\n   <td rowspan=\"2\" xss=removed>\r\n   <p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>mol CaC<sub>2</sub> =</span></span></span></p>\r\n   </td>\r\n   <td xss=removed>\r\n   <p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>128</span></span></span></p>\r\n   </td>\r\n   <td rowspan=\"2\" xss=removed>\r\n   <p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>= 2 mol</span></span></span></p>\r\n   </td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n   <td xss=removed>\r\n   <p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>64</span></span></span></p>\r\n   </td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Apabila CaC<sub>2</sub> yang bereaksi hanya 75 %, maka:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table\" xss=removed>\r\n <tbody>\r\n  <tr>\r\n   <td xss=removed>\r\n   <p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xs