n pemahaman terhadap kanker.</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Kebiasaan merokok merupakan resiko paling popular yang dikenali menurut hasil survey UICC</span></span></span></p>', 3, '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Kunci Jawabannya adalah </span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><strong>(C)</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Pembahasan</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Jawaban C tidak sesuai dengan kalimat (5) dan (6).</span></span></span></p>', '2020-12-08 02:40:02', '2020-12-08 02:40:02'),
(71, 6, 4, '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Konfigurasi unsur Y= 1s<sup>2</sup> 2s<sup>2</sup> 2p<sup>2 </sup>dan N= 1s<sup>2</sup> 2s<sup>2</sup> 2p<sup>6 </sup>3s<sup>2</sup> 3p<sup>5</sup> apabila membentuk senyawa memiliki tipe hibridisasi dan bentuk molekul berturut – turut.… </span></span></span>​​​​​​​</p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>sp<sup>3</sup>, tetrahedral</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>sp<sup>3</sup>, trigonal piramida</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>sp<sup>3 </sup>,<sup> </sup>bentuk V</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>sp<sup>3</sup>d, trigonal bipiramida</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>sp<sup>3</sup>d, seesaw</span></span></span></p>', 1, '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Senyawa yang dihasilkan: YN<sub>4</sub></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Y sebagai atom pusat, maka:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Y = 1s<sup>2</sup> <strong><span xss=removed>2s<sup>2</sup> 2p<sup>2 </sup>: elektron valensi: 2s<sup>2</sup> 2p<sup>2 </sup></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>1 elektron pada orbital s akan tereksitasi menuju orbital p, sehingga:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>1*     1*  1* 1*</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>__      __ __ __</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><strong><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Tipe hibridisasi    : sp<sup>3</sup></spa