(147, 10, 6, '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Untuk meningkatkan perekonomian nasional yang sedang lesu akibat tekanan ekonomi global dan juga mengantisipasi dampak keluarnya Inggris dari Uni Eropa ( Brexit ),  pemerintah berencana untuk melakukan kebijakan dibidang moneter. Berikut ini merupakan kebijakan moneter yang bersifat ekspansif, kecuali….</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Membeli kembali surat berharga milik pemerintah di masyarakat</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Menurunkan suku bunga bank</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Menurunkan cadangan kas yang ada di bank-bank umum</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Menjual surat-surat berharga</span></span></p>', '<p><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Mempermudah syarat pemberian pinjaman bank</span></span></span></p>', 4, '<p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><strong>Kebijakan Moneter ekspansif artinya kebijakan untuk menambah jumlah uang yang beredar, diantaranya:</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n <li xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Politik diskonto atau suku bunga  (</span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><em>Discount Policy</em></span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>), menurunkan suku bunga</span></span></span></li>\r\n <li xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Politik pasar terbuka (</span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><em>Open market policy</em></span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>), membeli surat-surat berharga</span></span></span></li>\r\n <li xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>Politik pagu kredi